WEBVTT

01:28.930 --> 01:35.030
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.430 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 3]

01:47.350 --> 01:48.680
What are you looking at?

02:03.710 --> 02:04.510
Do you like it?

02:07.290 --> 02:08.400
Thirty each.

02:08.740 --> 02:10.199
That's daylight robbery.

02:12.580 --> 02:14.530
You have to share a room with me.

02:14.650 --> 02:15.560
What bad luck.

02:15.890 --> 02:16.650
It's not like I insisted on

02:16.650 --> 02:17.910
moving into your room.

02:19.020 --> 02:20.740
Then just don't stay here.

02:21.250 --> 02:21.960
Anyway, now there's one extra person

02:21.960 --> 02:22.690
in this room.

02:22.860 --> 02:25.840
If I hadn't come, someone else
would've moved in anyway.

02:25.840 --> 02:26.710
I don't care.

02:27.300 --> 02:27.760
Anyway,

02:28.210 --> 02:30.010
you living here is annoying.

02:30.280 --> 02:32.110
You're being quite unreasonable.

02:32.110 --> 02:33.410
So what if I am?

02:34.210 --> 02:35.340
Have you had dinner?

02:36.100 --> 02:38.030
I have an audition. I'm not hungry.

02:39.740 --> 02:40.650
These clothes of mine

02:40.650 --> 02:42.710
are actually perfect for auditions.

02:42.950 --> 02:44.520
They're flashy and still decent.

02:44.520 --> 02:46.210
I have to charge more—50 a piece.

02:46.210 --> 02:47.740
You won't sell a single one.

02:47.970 --> 02:48.630
Don't worry.

02:48.630 --> 02:49.340
If there were an empty room,

02:49.340 --> 02:50.940
I would definitely move out.

02:52.540 --> 02:54.540
Don't make me wait forever for that.

03:13.730 --> 03:15.060
Mr. Zheng, long time no see.

03:15.060 --> 03:15.800
Yes, indeed.

03:15.960 --> 03:17.690
How are you and your wife doing?

03:17.840 --> 03:18.840
We're doing well.

03:19.360 --> 03:20.560
We're full of energy.

03:20.930 --> 03:21.730
How about you?

03:22.800 --> 03:23.610
Have you settled in?

03:23.610 --> 03:24.570
Where are you staying?

03:24.570 --> 03:25.970
I'm staying at a small hotel

03:25.970 --> 03:26.900
inside a hutong.

03:27.280 --> 03:27.710
OK.

03:28.650 --> 03:29.680
By the way, Mr. Zheng,

03:29.680 --> 03:30.730
this time I came,

03:30.840 --> 03:32.260
I plan to stay in Beijing.

03:32.470 --> 03:34.310
It's more convenient for my studies.

03:34.310 --> 03:35.900
Traveling back and forth before

03:35.900 --> 03:37.520
made it hard for me to learn properly.

03:37.520 --> 03:38.020
True.

03:38.630 --> 03:39.430
If you're planning to

03:39.430 --> 03:40.840
audition for orchestras

03:40.870 --> 03:42.530
or enter competitions later,

03:42.579 --> 03:43.579
you really do need

03:43.590 --> 03:45.320
more systematic improvement.

03:45.680 --> 03:47.610
Regular lessons are unavoidable.

03:47.740 --> 03:48.800
How about three classes a week?

03:48.800 --> 03:49.780
Of course, I'll give you a discount

03:49.780 --> 03:51.280
on tuition.

03:51.340 --> 03:52.600
Here, have some fruit!

03:54.090 --> 03:54.470
Come.

03:54.870 --> 03:55.280
Have some fruit.

03:55.280 --> 03:56.140
Zhuang Zhuang,

03:56.180 --> 03:57.110
have some fruit.

03:58.210 --> 03:59.140
Have some fruit.

03:59.340 --> 04:00.560
Thank you, Mrs. Zheng.

04:00.560 --> 04:01.190
When you're here,

04:01.190 --> 04:02.590
just make yourself at home.

04:02.590 --> 04:03.860
Please don't stand on ceremony.

04:03.860 --> 04:04.340
OK.

04:07.800 --> 04:08.930
That's really nice.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.740
You see, being young is great.

04:11.780 --> 04:13.310
She looks good in anything,

04:13.970 --> 04:14.970
right, Mr. Zheng?

04:16.040 --> 04:17.040
You look good too.

04:17.230 --> 04:18.630
You have your own beauty.

04:19.930 --> 04:21.190
You're never serious.

04:21.930 --> 04:23.600
How are your parents doing?

04:23.980 --> 04:25.110
They're doing well.

04:25.120 --> 04:26.680
They asked me to send you their regards.

04:26.680 --> 04:27.610
Really?

04:28.130 --> 04:29.660
Alright. When you go back home,

04:29.660 --> 04:31.100
say hello to them for me.

04:31.310 --> 04:31.680
OK.

04:31.820 --> 04:33.370
Alright, then I'll leave you to it.

04:33.370 --> 04:34.630
Mr. Zheng, time for class.

04:34.630 --> 04:35.310
Call me if you need anything.

04:35.310 --> 04:36.000
OK.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.240
Then let's get started.

04:38.240 --> 04:38.510
OK.

04:46.810 --> 04:52.000
When I was young, my mother told me that

04:52.370 --> 04:57.500
the sea is my hometown.

04:57.930 --> 05:02.810
Born by the sea,

05:03.180 --> 05:08.240
raised by the sea.

05:08.740 --> 05:14.010
Oh, ocean, ocean,

05:14.040 --> 05:19.040
is where I grew up.

05:19.420 --> 05:24.510
Sea breeze blows, waves surge,

05:24.800 --> 05:30.010
drifting with me.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.040
Very good.

05:32.680 --> 05:34.180
This take is much better than before.

05:34.180 --> 05:35.980
You've improved a lot.

05:37.310 --> 05:40.110
Let's start from the beginning
and do it once more.

05:44.430 --> 05:45.290
Mr. Zheng, I...

05:46.960 --> 05:47.760
What's wrong?

05:50.390 --> 05:51.590
Just speak your mind.

05:52.180 --> 05:52.620
OK.

05:54.220 --> 05:55.270
I... I was wondering

05:55.270 --> 05:55.930
if I could pay my tuition

05:55.930 --> 05:57.720
at the end of the month.

05:57.930 --> 05:59.190
Because my money

05:59.190 --> 06:00.830
was stolen at the train station.

06:00.830 --> 06:01.870
I've been looking for a job recently,

06:01.870 --> 06:02.800
and they all said

06:03.160 --> 06:04.570
that I wouldn't get paid

06:04.630 --> 06:06.090
until the end of the month.

06:08.190 --> 06:08.920
I see.

06:13.190 --> 06:14.520
Did you tell your family

06:14.560 --> 06:15.720
about this?

06:17.630 --> 06:19.250
Then how are you
paying for your accommodation?

06:19.250 --> 06:20.450
I earned a bit myself,

06:20.510 --> 06:22.170
and a friend helped me out too.

06:26.660 --> 06:27.450
Understood.

06:32.110 --> 06:32.810
Don't worry

06:33.659 --> 06:34.590
about the money.

06:35.190 --> 06:36.990
Let's focus on the lesson first.

06:38.890 --> 06:40.090
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

06:42.220 --> 06:43.390
Do you even know how to play?

06:43.390 --> 06:44.010
We two are playing chess here;

06:44.010 --> 06:45.070
stop running your mouth like a donkey.

06:45.070 --> 06:46.930
You're the donkey—
you don't even know

06:46.930 --> 06:47.590
how to play.

06:49.050 --> 06:50.960
Isn't this my famous little sister?

06:49.180 --> 06:51.610
[Bookstore]

06:51.770 --> 06:52.750
Where are you going?

06:52.750 --> 06:53.810
I have things to do.

06:56.000 --> 06:58.210
Hey… Did you guys drive

06:58.300 --> 07:00.360
the person in your room away already?

07:00.620 --> 07:01.750
There are too many people
in the courtyard.

07:01.750 --> 07:02.860
It's not convenient to talk.

07:02.860 --> 07:03.450
I was just about to

07:03.450 --> 07:04.870
report the situation to you.

07:04.870 --> 07:05.810
You can't rush this.

07:05.810 --> 07:07.000
It's like pulling nails.

07:07.000 --> 07:08.160
You have to pull bit by bit.

07:08.160 --> 07:09.290
If you pull too fast,

07:09.600 --> 07:10.190
it snaps.

07:10.950 --> 07:12.410
So how far have you pulled?

07:12.510 --> 07:13.500
I just pulled it out,

07:13.500 --> 07:15.660
but it went back in.

07:16.130 --> 07:16.810
I've got something to do,
so I'll head off first.

07:16.810 --> 07:18.120
Wait, wait.

07:19.240 --> 07:20.370
Where are you going?

07:21.510 --> 07:22.570
That place up ahead

07:22.630 --> 07:23.680
sells door-knocker beef pancakes.

07:23.680 --> 07:25.500
You haven't eaten yet, have you?
I'll treat you.

07:25.500 --> 07:27.130
I... Thanks.

07:27.450 --> 07:28.680
But I can't eat anything lately.

07:28.680 --> 07:30.630
I have to lose weight for an audition.

07:30.630 --> 07:31.860
Stop trying to lose weight.

07:31.860 --> 07:33.810
You're already as thin as a rake.

07:33.980 --> 07:35.220
Excuse you?

07:35.330 --> 07:36.450
I'm not being rude.

07:36.680 --> 07:37.620
Look at those skinny arms

07:37.620 --> 07:38.750
and legs of yours—

07:39.120 --> 07:39.980
one strong wind

07:40.890 --> 07:42.220
and you'll snap in half.

07:43.060 --> 07:44.120
Are you mocking me?

07:44.360 --> 07:46.000
If I really snap in half out here

07:46.000 --> 07:47.000
and get stuck in the motel,

07:47.000 --> 07:47.860
will you take care of me?

07:47.860 --> 07:48.860
I'll take care of you.

07:48.860 --> 07:49.830
I have a bike.

07:49.860 --> 07:50.590
I'll sell it.

07:50.680 --> 07:52.330
And I can sell my saxophone too.

07:52.330 --> 07:54.060
I can even cover your rent for you.

07:54.060 --> 07:55.070
But then again,

07:55.680 --> 07:57.510
with your family background,

07:57.540 --> 08:00.130
you probably wouldn't let me pay anyway.

08:00.130 --> 08:01.160
I'm just trying to show

08:01.160 --> 08:01.960
my sincerity.

08:03.360 --> 08:03.890
Let's go.

08:06.630 --> 08:08.180
I've already made plans with someone.

08:08.180 --> 08:09.640
Let's do it some other day.

08:14.250 --> 08:15.420
Have a bite.

08:18.930 --> 08:20.600
Even if everything goes wrong,

08:20.600 --> 08:22.800
you should still take care of yourself.

08:22.930 --> 08:24.860
You have to look on the bright side.

08:25.110 --> 08:27.630
I failed the audition this time,

08:28.300 --> 08:29.700
not because of my acting,

08:30.160 --> 08:32.289
but because the director has no taste.

08:33.710 --> 08:35.100
You're blaming the director?

08:35.100 --> 08:36.559
You're getting bold, huh?

08:37.240 --> 08:38.169
You're really something.

08:38.169 --> 08:40.230
Seriously, who gave you the courage?

08:41.669 --> 08:42.100
Wait, look.

08:42.100 --> 08:43.700
Let's not talk about acting.

08:44.740 --> 08:45.220
Look.

08:45.240 --> 08:46.110
Take a look.

08:46.370 --> 08:47.720
What are you wearing?

08:50.120 --> 08:52.610
This outfit is perfectly fine.

08:53.290 --> 08:54.820
What are you talking about?

08:54.890 --> 08:56.320
I said my outfit

08:56.340 --> 08:57.400
is perfectly fine.

08:58.600 --> 09:00.400
It's about coordination, girl.

09:00.440 --> 09:02.030
Coordination matters, girl.

09:02.030 --> 09:03.740
Taste is also crucial for an actor.

09:03.740 --> 09:04.420
Girl,

09:04.670 --> 09:06.870
people judge you by what you wear first.

09:07.860 --> 09:08.460
I've told you so much,

09:08.460 --> 09:09.150
but you probably can't even take it in.

09:09.150 --> 09:09.770
Go back

09:09.770 --> 09:11.300
and think it over yourself.

09:40.410 --> 09:42.840
[We hope you enjoy your stay here.]

09:52.720 --> 09:53.220
Zhuang,

09:53.330 --> 09:54.390
have you eaten yet?

09:54.580 --> 09:55.480
Are you hungry?

09:55.700 --> 09:57.230
I bought a lot of food.

09:58.010 --> 09:59.280
This Beijing meat roll

09:59.410 --> 10:00.210
is delicious.

10:00.600 --> 10:01.600
Have you tried it?

10:01.790 --> 10:04.050
It's like a dough roll

10:04.260 --> 10:05.480
with meat filling inside.

10:05.480 --> 10:05.860
Here.

10:06.340 --> 10:06.790
Try it.

10:09.010 --> 10:09.970
It smells great.

10:10.080 --> 10:10.940
It's still hot.

10:20.810 --> 10:22.730
And there's traditional Beijing yogurt

10:22.730 --> 10:23.860
in a ceramic bottle.

10:28.530 --> 10:29.340
Try it.

10:30.480 --> 10:32.080
What's wrong with you today?

10:35.890 --> 10:36.490
Is it good?

10:38.630 --> 10:39.630
It's pretty good.

10:42.770 --> 10:43.240
Zhuang,

10:43.650 --> 10:45.180
you've got such good taste.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.630
No wonder the clothes you wear

10:46.630 --> 10:47.550
always look amazing,

10:47.550 --> 10:49.240
just like those in magazines.

10:49.860 --> 10:51.030
There are lots more magazines here.

10:51.030 --> 10:52.250
Read them if you like.

10:53.000 --> 10:53.370
OK.

11:01.480 --> 11:02.100
You know,

11:02.550 --> 11:03.740
dressing

11:04.290 --> 11:05.510
is kind of an art.

11:07.120 --> 11:08.820
The other day I went for an audition,

11:08.820 --> 11:10.000
and the assistant director told me

11:10.000 --> 11:11.780
to dress better next time.

11:12.410 --> 11:12.860
I

11:12.890 --> 11:14.610
walked around the streets

11:14.910 --> 11:16.000
trying to buy something nice,

11:16.000 --> 11:17.130
but I couldn't find anything
that looked good.

11:17.130 --> 11:18.840
I don't know how to
match clothes properly.

11:18.840 --> 11:20.580
I got so frustrated that I just ended up
buying a bunch of snacks instead.

11:20.580 --> 11:21.770
What role were you auditioning for?

11:21.770 --> 11:22.700
Tell me about it.

11:22.790 --> 11:24.130
I'll help you figure it out.

11:24.130 --> 11:26.390
It's kind of a vintage-style

11:26.500 --> 11:27.670
singing diva,

11:27.820 --> 11:29.890
and also that very bright,

11:29.910 --> 11:31.310
modern urban woman look,

11:31.340 --> 11:31.870
and

11:32.120 --> 11:33.650
-a office type...
-Hold on.

11:42.380 --> 11:43.040
I actually

11:43.320 --> 11:44.200
put together a few outfits

11:44.200 --> 11:45.390
the other day.

11:46.410 --> 11:47.010
Take a look

11:47.480 --> 11:49.140
and see if you like any of them.

11:51.060 --> 11:52.190
They all look great.

11:52.440 --> 11:53.100
Try them on.

11:53.340 --> 11:53.650
I...

11:54.940 --> 11:56.480
Is this really appropriate?

11:56.480 --> 11:57.440
Just try them.

11:57.530 --> 11:59.060
You've got such a great figure anyway—

11:59.060 --> 12:00.460
just think of it as helping me out
as a model.

12:00.460 --> 12:00.910
Sure.

12:01.780 --> 12:03.040
See which one you like.

12:04.650 --> 12:06.180
I think this one looks good.

12:15.170 --> 12:15.700
How is it?

12:17.600 --> 12:18.400
It looks good.

12:19.620 --> 12:21.580
You look so vibrant in bright colors.

12:21.580 --> 12:22.170
Really?

12:23.220 --> 12:23.550
Here.

12:30.240 --> 12:31.770
With this belt,

12:31.810 --> 12:33.340
it really looks different.

12:33.410 --> 12:35.870
If you like it, just take it
and wear it for a couple of days.

12:35.870 --> 12:37.270
Any others that you like?

12:38.780 --> 12:39.500
They all look good.

12:39.500 --> 12:40.630
And these jeans—

12:40.940 --> 12:43.030
the fit is amazing.

12:43.720 --> 12:46.050
I've never seen a cut
like this on the street.

12:46.050 --> 12:47.390
This would go well with this top—

12:47.390 --> 12:48.250
the purple one.

12:49.530 --> 12:49.870
OK.

12:57.360 --> 12:57.820
Zhuang,

12:58.340 --> 13:00.800
I find your accent
really familiar and kind.

13:02.080 --> 13:03.320
You're from Zhejiang too, right?

13:03.320 --> 13:04.520
Yes, I'm from Huzhou.

13:04.860 --> 13:05.860
I'm from Wenzhou.

13:06.150 --> 13:07.950
So we're from the same province.

13:11.550 --> 13:12.370
You should wear

13:12.370 --> 13:13.340
more bright colors—

13:13.340 --> 13:14.540
they really suit you.

13:14.770 --> 13:15.550
I think so.

13:17.080 --> 13:18.140
Thank you, Zhuang.

13:20.390 --> 13:21.320
You're welcome.

13:24.250 --> 13:28.500
Ah.

13:28.670 --> 13:29.630
Very good.

13:30.320 --> 13:34.720
Ah.

13:35.290 --> 13:36.310
Open your mouth.

13:37.100 --> 13:39.720
Ah.

13:39.770 --> 13:42.490
Open your mouth. Hold on.

13:42.530 --> 13:44.320
Good. Very good.

13:48.120 --> 13:48.960
Stop fighting.

13:48.960 --> 13:49.870
-What are you doing?
-Stop! Stop!

13:49.870 --> 13:50.480
Watch out.

13:50.720 --> 13:51.580
Stop fighting.

13:53.130 --> 13:53.630
Are you okay?

13:53.630 --> 13:54.060
Son.

13:54.670 --> 13:55.000
Son.

13:55.000 --> 13:56.130
Where did you get hurt?

13:56.130 --> 13:56.550
Son.

13:56.550 --> 13:56.840
Are you okay?

13:56.840 --> 13:57.290
Let go!

13:57.410 --> 13:59.010
What kind of teacher are you?

13:59.430 --> 14:00.890
-Son, does it hurt?
-He hit me first.

14:00.890 --> 14:01.580
Where did you get hit?

14:01.580 --> 14:02.940
Tell Mom, where does it hurt?

14:02.940 --> 14:03.670
My arm hurts.

14:03.860 --> 14:04.100
You...

14:04.100 --> 14:04.830
My arm hurts.

14:05.030 --> 14:06.120
How are you taking care of the kids?

14:06.120 --> 14:07.220
Why did you grab him like that?

14:07.220 --> 14:08.530
-I was trying to separate them.
-Stop explaining.

14:08.530 --> 14:09.530
I saw everything.

14:09.750 --> 14:11.100
Go get the principal here right now!

14:11.100 --> 14:12.290
What is going on?

14:12.370 --> 14:13.970
Can you even teach properly?

14:14.010 --> 14:15.410
How could you hit a child?

14:15.410 --> 14:16.760
I didn't.

14:16.870 --> 14:18.530
They were shoving each other.

14:18.740 --> 14:20.190
Did you grab him?

14:23.250 --> 14:23.970
Yes.

14:24.480 --> 14:25.170
I did grab them.

14:25.170 --> 14:25.720
But I was trying to

14:25.720 --> 14:26.650
separate them.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.340
The parents

14:28.390 --> 14:29.840
were watching right there.

14:29.840 --> 14:30.410
Anyway, under no circumstances

14:30.410 --> 14:31.390
should there be any physical contact

14:31.390 --> 14:32.450
with the children.

14:32.630 --> 14:33.870
Haven't you taught kids before?

14:33.870 --> 14:36.200
Don't you understand something so basic?

14:39.440 --> 14:40.500
All right, that's enough.

14:40.500 --> 14:41.330
I don't think

14:41.390 --> 14:42.860
you're suitable for this job.

14:42.860 --> 14:44.000
The parent is now

14:44.030 --> 14:45.670
refusing to let it go
and demanding a refund.

14:45.670 --> 14:46.750
You should just leave.

14:46.750 --> 14:47.770
It's not that I'm unsuitable for it.

14:47.770 --> 14:48.700
It's just that in that situation,

14:48.700 --> 14:49.220
I really had to...

14:49.220 --> 14:50.690
Stop explaining!

14:51.100 --> 14:52.930
The parents saw everything.

14:53.150 --> 14:54.220
You're still on probation—

14:54.220 --> 14:54.960
no pay.

14:56.410 --> 14:57.770
Please give me another chance,

14:57.770 --> 14:58.490
will you?

14:59.340 --> 15:00.680
I'll say it again.

15:00.980 --> 15:02.600
You're not suitable for this job.

15:02.600 --> 15:03.430
I promise that

15:03.530 --> 15:04.460
if the child acts up again,

15:04.460 --> 15:05.860
I'll handle it properly.

15:06.340 --> 15:07.050
If something like this happens again,

15:07.050 --> 15:08.270
I'll leave on my own.

15:08.910 --> 15:09.290
OK?

15:12.080 --> 15:13.210
But even if I agreed,

15:13.370 --> 15:14.120
how am I supposed to explain this

15:14.120 --> 15:14.980
to the parents?

15:15.410 --> 15:16.870
I'll go apologize to them.

15:17.240 --> 15:18.700
I'll go apologize to them.

15:22.140 --> 15:24.390
-Scissors, rock, paper…
-I'm really sorry about today.

15:24.390 --> 15:25.430
It was my fault.

15:25.540 --> 15:26.250
I hope you can

15:26.250 --> 15:27.680
give me another chance, will you?

15:27.680 --> 15:28.370
I promise it won't

15:28.370 --> 15:29.320
happen again.

15:29.320 --> 15:30.690
You don't need to apologize to us.

15:30.690 --> 15:31.560
It's useless.

15:31.700 --> 15:32.120
Yes.

15:32.140 --> 15:33.980
We're definitely going to change teachers.

15:33.980 --> 15:35.460
Luckily, the child
wasn't seriously injured.

15:35.460 --> 15:36.100
If anything had happened,

15:36.100 --> 15:37.010
your whole training center

15:37.010 --> 15:37.860
wouldn't have been able to
afford the compensation.

15:37.860 --> 15:38.440
Exactly.

15:39.120 --> 15:40.030
What bad luck.

15:41.120 --> 15:41.650
As a teacher,

15:41.650 --> 15:44.200
you need to be a bit
more patient in the future, alright?

15:44.200 --> 15:44.480
Come on.

15:44.480 --> 15:45.080
Auntie Li,

15:45.530 --> 15:46.830
how old is your child?

15:47.030 --> 15:47.630
Eight.

15:47.740 --> 15:48.410
Eight?

15:54.600 --> 15:55.860
Why are you here again?

15:56.200 --> 15:58.630
We don't know
when Director Weng will be back.

15:58.630 --> 16:00.290
Why don't you wait by the door?

16:18.000 --> 16:18.840
Are you still waiting there?

16:18.840 --> 16:19.360
Mr. Wu.

16:20.390 --> 16:21.650
Alright, I'm off work.

16:43.000 --> 16:43.660
Xu Shengli.

16:45.100 --> 16:45.760
Hello, sir.

16:46.420 --> 16:48.820
Don't come back
for the next couple of days.

16:48.980 --> 16:50.040
Director Weng is away on business.

16:50.040 --> 16:50.960
We don't know when

16:50.960 --> 16:51.760
he'll be back.

16:52.030 --> 16:53.090
On a business trip?

16:53.170 --> 16:54.200
Then... They...

16:54.960 --> 16:56.820
They didn't mean to mess with you.

16:57.010 --> 16:57.870
You know,

16:58.360 --> 16:59.910
there are many people

16:59.960 --> 17:01.170
coming to see Director Weng every day.

17:01.170 --> 17:03.370
Some just use it as an excuse

17:03.860 --> 17:05.060
to hand over scripts.

17:05.250 --> 17:06.609
It's led to a lot of jokes

17:06.660 --> 17:08.260
and ridiculous situations.

17:09.900 --> 17:10.579
Mr. Zou,

17:11.720 --> 17:13.450
Director Weng really knows me.

17:13.790 --> 17:14.790
We've worked together

17:14.790 --> 17:15.589
before.

17:17.000 --> 17:18.530
I even have a photo with him,

17:21.240 --> 17:22.609
and he's also said

17:23.000 --> 17:24.460
my writing is really good.

17:25.680 --> 17:26.280
Young man,

17:26.940 --> 17:29.540
it doesn't matter
whether I believe you or not.

17:29.900 --> 17:32.510
What matters is that
you need to understand something.

17:32.510 --> 17:33.500
Understand what exactly?

17:33.500 --> 17:34.570
I understand that

17:35.640 --> 17:36.820
you love writing

17:37.140 --> 17:38.810
and want to be an artistic young man—

17:38.810 --> 17:39.700
there's nothing wrong with that.

17:39.700 --> 17:40.940
As a hobby writer,

17:41.270 --> 17:43.090
I think your work

17:43.850 --> 17:45.400
is quite good.

17:47.310 --> 17:49.400
But if you want to make a living

17:49.610 --> 17:50.610
from writing,

17:51.350 --> 17:53.550
that's a completely different matter.

17:54.330 --> 17:55.330
Someone like you,

17:55.830 --> 17:57.420
turning a hobby into competition

17:57.420 --> 17:59.220
for other people's livelihood,

17:59.660 --> 18:01.190
is only setting yourself up

18:01.510 --> 18:03.440
for trouble.

18:03.880 --> 18:04.920
Take my advice.

18:05.310 --> 18:07.340
Keep writing

18:07.770 --> 18:08.860
as a hobby;

18:09.500 --> 18:10.110
that way,

18:11.030 --> 18:13.290
you might actually find real happiness.

18:14.750 --> 18:15.480
I'm leaving.

18:17.960 --> 18:18.460
Mr. Zou,

18:20.590 --> 18:21.570
please wait.

18:33.850 --> 18:34.510
Mr. Zou,

18:35.350 --> 18:36.480
here is my address

18:35.460 --> 18:37.650
[Seasons Change Hotel
—Xu Shengli]

18:36.480 --> 18:37.720
and phone number in Beijing.

18:37.720 --> 18:39.160
If Director Weng returns,

18:39.160 --> 18:39.590
or

18:40.200 --> 18:42.730
if you have any suggestions
about the script,

18:42.810 --> 18:44.300
please feel free to contact me anytime.

18:44.300 --> 18:47.460
[Seasons Change Hotel
—Xu Shengli]

18:55.310 --> 18:56.040
I'm leaving.

19:06.500 --> 19:06.910
Xu.

19:10.180 --> 19:11.040
Zhuang Zhuang.

19:11.810 --> 19:13.330
Why do you look so down?

19:14.160 --> 19:15.110
No.

19:15.530 --> 19:15.900
No.

19:16.610 --> 19:17.930
I've been out all day.

19:18.140 --> 19:19.200
I'm a little tired.

19:22.420 --> 19:24.110
You've just arrived in Beijing.

19:24.110 --> 19:25.280
You should cheer up.

19:26.810 --> 19:29.180
Be positive and full of hope.

19:30.880 --> 19:31.350
Yes.

19:31.980 --> 19:33.200
Be positive

19:33.850 --> 19:36.200
and full of hope!

19:37.700 --> 19:38.960
What are you doing? Xu!

19:39.200 --> 19:40.070
What are you doing?

19:40.070 --> 19:40.750
Don't shout.

19:40.750 --> 19:41.150
You...

19:42.090 --> 19:42.550
Shut up!

19:42.790 --> 19:43.480
Help!

19:43.500 --> 19:44.250
Don't shout!

19:45.110 --> 19:46.040
What's going on?

19:46.160 --> 19:47.070
They're fighting?

19:47.070 --> 19:47.440
They're fighting?

19:47.440 --> 19:48.500
They're fighting.

19:50.440 --> 19:51.500
Help!

19:51.660 --> 19:52.390
Don't shout.

19:54.480 --> 19:55.630
What a deep grudge.

19:55.920 --> 19:56.770
Who? Who is it?

19:56.980 --> 19:57.510
Who is it?

19:57.830 --> 19:58.790
Xu.

19:59.010 --> 20:00.000
Which Xu guy?

20:00.750 --> 20:01.860
Xu Shengli.

20:06.580 --> 20:07.640
Are we going in or not?

20:07.640 --> 20:08.320
We go in!

20:08.760 --> 20:09.960
Little Northeasterner!

20:09.960 --> 20:10.550
Don't shout.

20:10.550 --> 20:11.250
Bro.

20:14.140 --> 20:14.720
Help!

20:14.810 --> 20:15.880
Hitting women isn't right.

20:15.880 --> 20:16.830
Go! Grab your gear.

20:16.830 --> 20:17.360
Let's go.

20:18.790 --> 20:19.320
Bro.

20:19.460 --> 20:20.310
Bro, over here.

20:20.310 --> 20:21.000
Let go!

20:21.570 --> 20:23.650
Little Northeasterner!

20:26.120 --> 20:27.120
The money is here.

20:27.780 --> 20:28.370
Go away!

20:28.850 --> 20:30.960
Go away! Get away!

20:31.010 --> 20:31.590
Go away!

20:32.640 --> 20:33.300
Who is that?

20:33.880 --> 20:34.680
What are you doing?

20:34.680 --> 20:35.550
-Stop!
-Stop!

20:35.640 --> 20:36.250
Stand right there!

20:36.250 --> 20:37.050
Go, go, go! Hurry!

20:37.050 --> 20:37.650
Don't run!

20:37.680 --> 20:38.610
Don't run!

20:39.400 --> 20:40.000
Don't run!

20:40.850 --> 20:42.700
Charge!

20:42.920 --> 20:43.350
Stop!

20:43.380 --> 20:43.740
Don't run!

20:43.740 --> 20:44.880
Charge!

20:44.980 --> 20:45.910
Xu! Xu!

20:46.270 --> 20:46.850
Xu!

20:48.530 --> 20:49.570
My money!

20:52.640 --> 20:53.270
Xu!

20:54.670 --> 20:55.620
Somebody help!

20:56.900 --> 20:57.400
Xu!

21:01.820 --> 21:03.720
Thanks for saving me just now.

21:04.050 --> 21:04.710
No problem.

21:05.500 --> 21:06.660
We weren't even trying to save you;

21:06.660 --> 21:08.330
we were just saving the beauty.

21:08.330 --> 21:09.120
Tang,

21:09.310 --> 21:11.310
-I've seen robbers on the street,
-The police are here.

21:11.310 --> 21:12.290
but I've never seen anyone

21:12.290 --> 21:13.090
beat someone this badly.

21:13.090 --> 21:13.680
So I think

21:13.680 --> 21:14.770
this might be a revenge case.

21:14.770 --> 21:15.660
The person who got beaten

21:15.660 --> 21:16.570
looks pretty honest.

21:16.570 --> 21:18.050
He doesn't seem like someone
who would cause this kind of trouble.

21:18.050 --> 21:19.010
So, I think...

21:19.010 --> 21:20.250
What do you mean by "you think?"

21:20.250 --> 21:21.330
You've gotten quite capable lately,

21:21.330 --> 21:21.880
haven't you?

21:21.880 --> 21:23.140
You're solving cases now?

21:23.140 --> 21:24.200
I wouldn't dare to.

21:24.590 --> 21:25.250
That's him.

21:26.110 --> 21:26.750
Officer Tang.

21:26.750 --> 21:27.200
You're here.

21:27.200 --> 21:28.740
Are you lining up to welcome me?

21:28.740 --> 21:29.110
Yes.

21:30.140 --> 21:31.090
You must be Xu Shengli?

21:31.090 --> 21:31.400
Yes.

21:31.460 --> 21:32.460
Here, have a seat.

21:34.720 --> 21:35.660
Is your head okay?

21:35.660 --> 21:37.380
I'm fine, I just got it bandaged.

21:37.380 --> 21:38.010
Could you cooperate with us

21:38.010 --> 21:38.790
and tell us what happened?

21:38.790 --> 21:40.450
No problem. No problem at all.

21:41.790 --> 21:43.240
Did you see clearly who hit you?

21:43.240 --> 21:44.170
Do you know them?

21:44.790 --> 21:46.060
He came up from behind

21:46.140 --> 21:47.110
and hit me with a stick.

21:47.110 --> 21:48.090
My vision went black,

21:48.090 --> 21:49.550
I... I didn't see clearly.

21:49.640 --> 21:51.010
How many of them were there?

21:51.010 --> 21:52.890
About three or four.

21:53.030 --> 21:53.380
Yeah.

21:54.240 --> 21:55.770
How much did they take from you?

21:55.770 --> 21:57.040
They took 1,500 yuan.

21:57.740 --> 21:58.900
Were you guys at the scene too?

21:58.900 --> 21:59.250
No,

21:59.270 --> 22:01.400
They were gone by the time we got there.

22:01.420 --> 22:03.020
I was there. I saw it.

22:04.250 --> 22:05.250
You live here too?

22:06.160 --> 22:06.970
Officer,

22:07.180 --> 22:08.580
I think this was revenge.

22:10.310 --> 22:10.940
Revenge?

22:12.330 --> 22:13.610
Two of them looked exactly like

22:13.610 --> 22:14.920
the people who stole my wallet

22:14.920 --> 22:16.460
a couple of days ago at the train station.

22:16.460 --> 22:16.880
Xu,

22:16.900 --> 22:18.180
you even helped me chase them then.

22:18.180 --> 22:20.040
Maybe they were holding a grudge.

22:20.160 --> 22:20.420
Yes.

22:21.570 --> 22:23.140
That's quite something, young lady.

22:23.140 --> 22:24.800
That's a very important lead.

22:25.220 --> 22:26.150
Write that down.

22:29.850 --> 22:30.380
Alright.

22:30.810 --> 22:31.550
Alright, we've noted down

22:31.550 --> 22:32.550
your statements.

22:32.640 --> 22:34.660
We'll notify you if there's any news.

22:34.660 --> 22:36.250
Are these two long-term residents here?

22:36.250 --> 22:36.920
They just moved in.

22:36.920 --> 22:38.720
They just paid one month's rent.

22:38.750 --> 22:40.680
Everyone who comes here is a guest.

22:40.700 --> 22:41.920
Don't just take their money.

22:41.920 --> 22:44.250
Make sure you also
take care of them properly.

22:44.250 --> 22:46.110
You all should be more attentive.

22:46.960 --> 22:47.680
Get some rest.

22:47.680 --> 22:48.680
Wait for our news.

22:49.300 --> 22:49.630
Sure.

22:49.740 --> 22:50.810
Everyone, take it easy.

22:50.810 --> 22:51.900
Thank you, Officer.

22:51.900 --> 22:52.400
Thank you.

22:52.400 --> 22:53.000
Thank you.

22:53.010 --> 22:53.480
Goodbye.

22:53.480 --> 22:54.810
I'll walk you out, Tang.

22:55.460 --> 22:56.030
Xu!

22:56.140 --> 22:56.540
Hurry.

22:57.790 --> 22:58.420
What's going on?

22:58.420 --> 22:59.080
Xu Shengli.

22:59.420 --> 23:03.100
[Guest Room]

23:03.170 --> 23:06.650
[Seasons Change Hotel]

23:06.700 --> 23:07.830
Why isn't he snoring

23:07.850 --> 23:08.930
or grind his teeth?

23:09.050 --> 23:09.900
He's been asleep for a day and a night.

23:09.900 --> 23:10.890
He's practically glued to the bed.

23:10.890 --> 23:12.460
He really thinks he's a big shot.

23:12.460 --> 23:12.810
With a hit like that

23:12.810 --> 23:13.660
to his head,

23:13.660 --> 23:14.720
could it affect his brain?

23:14.720 --> 23:16.700
-It's fine. It's fine.
-From now on...

23:16.700 --> 23:17.720
Who hasn't been beaten up before?

23:17.720 --> 23:18.350
Wake up.

23:18.380 --> 23:19.600
But I keep saying...

23:20.740 --> 23:21.500
Move aside.

23:22.310 --> 23:23.840
Can you stop bothering him?

23:25.740 --> 23:27.400
Let me make it thicker for you.

23:41.830 --> 23:42.420
Xu,

23:43.140 --> 23:44.270
take your medicine.

23:50.720 --> 23:51.780
I don't want to eat.

23:55.160 --> 23:56.620
Then do you want some food?

23:58.460 --> 23:59.370
No.

23:59.720 --> 24:00.460
Or else,

24:00.510 --> 24:02.330
tell her what you want.

24:03.720 --> 24:04.250
Miss,

24:04.810 --> 24:07.070
maybe we should take him to the hospital.

24:07.350 --> 24:09.010
Don't let that writer's brain

24:09.140 --> 24:11.140
get damaged from getting beaten up.

24:11.200 --> 24:12.250
Why go to a hospital?

24:12.250 --> 24:13.370
It's not as comfortable as here.

24:13.370 --> 24:14.330
Right? He's been taken care of
in the room.

24:14.330 --> 24:15.330
This is better than…

24:15.330 --> 24:16.790
Taking him away works too.

24:18.010 --> 24:20.070
Do you guys have nothing better to do?

24:20.660 --> 24:21.420
Don't you have anything upsetting going on

24:21.420 --> 24:22.610
in your own lives?

24:22.960 --> 24:23.460
Miss,

24:24.350 --> 24:26.000
just being alive is already

24:26.000 --> 24:26.730
a hard thing.

24:26.770 --> 24:27.880
Raphael, Michelangelo,

24:27.880 --> 24:28.850
Leonardo da Vinci—

24:28.850 --> 24:29.550
nowadays we see them

24:29.550 --> 24:30.830
as great artists,

24:30.850 --> 24:31.250
right?

24:31.610 --> 24:32.270
But back then,

24:32.270 --> 24:35.330
they were basically just
working for the aristocrats.

24:35.400 --> 24:37.030
If you want to heal your soul,
you've got to listen to some music.

24:37.030 --> 24:37.970
Ignore them.

24:38.070 --> 24:39.500
I'll go get you something to eat.

24:39.500 --> 24:41.000
You know, Plato—

24:41.070 --> 24:41.570
well, maybe it was

24:41.570 --> 24:42.510
Aristotle—once said that

24:42.510 --> 24:44.940
suffering is the best soil

24:45.070 --> 24:46.310
for nourishing art.

24:46.510 --> 24:47.920
Here, let me show you

24:47.960 --> 24:49.640
what Bach's sense of humor is like.

24:49.640 --> 24:52.090
There is actually a misconception here.

24:52.110 --> 24:54.290
Seriousness isn't all there

24:54.380 --> 24:55.440
is to Bach's music.

24:55.480 --> 24:56.540
Don't just read it.

25:55.820 --> 26:00.150
[Notes in motion,
chasing dreams without ever stopping.]

26:02.310 --> 26:03.250
Have you eaten, Little Northeasterner?

26:03.250 --> 26:03.890
Are you heading out?

26:03.790 --> 26:12.300
[A home away from home, only better.]

26:03.960 --> 26:05.220
I have something to do.

26:12.350 --> 26:20.960
[Guest Room]

26:14.180 --> 26:15.510
Come on, Zhuang Zhuang.

26:15.980 --> 26:16.640
Ms. Zhuang,

26:17.000 --> 26:19.070
are you heading off
to teach the kids again?

26:19.070 --> 26:19.720
No.

26:20.090 --> 26:20.850
I got fired.

26:21.720 --> 26:23.720
You got fired and you're this happy?

26:23.790 --> 26:25.090
So you found a new job?

26:25.250 --> 26:25.930
Not yet.

26:26.200 --> 26:27.010
I'm just about to head out

26:27.010 --> 26:27.930
and look for it.

26:28.000 --> 26:29.200
Maybe I'll get lucky.

26:29.250 --> 26:29.810
Go ahead.

26:29.310 --> 26:34.060
[Guest Room]

26:30.480 --> 26:32.410
I should learn from your attitude.

26:32.790 --> 26:33.570
By the way,

26:34.550 --> 26:35.420
tell Xu

26:35.420 --> 26:36.740
that he hasn't fully recovered yet,

26:36.740 --> 26:39.000
so he shouldn't go out unless necessary.

26:39.660 --> 26:40.320
Ms. Zhuang,

26:40.790 --> 26:41.990
you're a good person.

26:42.080 --> 26:43.460
He's a good person too.

26:44.190 --> 26:46.120
But let me say a couple more things:

26:46.530 --> 26:47.440
sometimes

26:47.530 --> 26:48.790
you can't take a man's vulnerability

26:48.790 --> 26:49.650
too seriously.

26:50.330 --> 26:51.530
Right now his head is full of

26:51.530 --> 26:53.000
sentimental things.

26:53.440 --> 26:56.040
Once he gets better,
he'll forget all about it.

26:56.530 --> 26:57.660
That would be great.

26:58.510 --> 27:00.440
Isn't it good for him to get better?

27:02.250 --> 27:03.580
Remember to remind him.

27:06.530 --> 27:07.140
OK.

27:20.290 --> 27:20.890
Very good.

27:21.550 --> 27:22.550
The class today

27:23.160 --> 27:24.140
was of high quality.

27:24.140 --> 27:25.680
It shows you kept my pointers

27:25.680 --> 27:26.550
in mind

27:26.640 --> 27:27.510
while singing.

27:27.880 --> 27:28.680
That's great.

27:29.440 --> 27:31.830
Okay, let's continue. Come on.

27:35.770 --> 27:36.370
Mr. Zheng,

27:36.590 --> 27:37.520
I wanted to ask,

27:37.660 --> 27:38.990
if you know of any need

27:39.220 --> 27:40.240
for recording backing vocals

27:40.240 --> 27:41.970
or vocal teaching assistants.

27:47.750 --> 27:48.640
I see.

27:49.610 --> 27:50.470
Zhuang Zhuang,

27:51.840 --> 27:54.500
you're thinking that
since you're already out here,

27:54.500 --> 27:55.500
you should do more

27:56.100 --> 27:56.790
to help your family

27:56.790 --> 27:58.060
lighten the burden.

27:58.770 --> 27:59.570
I understand.

28:00.310 --> 28:01.400
But you must know,

28:01.790 --> 28:02.420
you are different from

28:02.420 --> 28:04.080
the kids at the conservatory.

28:04.550 --> 28:05.880
Now is the most critical moment

28:05.880 --> 28:07.240
for your competition prep

28:07.240 --> 28:08.810
and troupe audition.

28:10.810 --> 28:11.700
You must pay special attention

28:11.700 --> 28:13.160
to protecting your voice.

28:13.180 --> 28:14.140
Our daily practice

28:14.140 --> 28:15.380
is already very draining.

28:15.380 --> 28:17.140
If you go out to sing

28:17.200 --> 28:17.960
or work,

28:20.220 --> 28:21.420
I'll be very worried.

28:22.940 --> 28:23.740
I understand.

28:28.240 --> 28:29.100
Zhuang Zhuang,

28:30.380 --> 28:31.270
don't worry

28:32.380 --> 28:33.440
about the tuition.

28:34.440 --> 28:36.370
Just focus on your lessons for now.

28:37.130 --> 28:38.330
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

28:40.420 --> 28:42.050
-Sign it.
-Little Northeasterner.

28:42.050 --> 28:43.570
Where is my letter?

28:43.570 --> 28:44.440
You're in high spirits.

28:44.440 --> 28:45.480
Is your head better?

28:45.480 --> 28:46.810
I'm sharp.

28:46.900 --> 28:47.510
Look.

28:50.070 --> 28:50.830
Your moneymaker.

28:50.830 --> 28:52.030
You gotta protect it.

28:53.290 --> 28:54.140
This is a registered letter.

28:54.140 --> 28:55.220
I had to keep it separate for you.

28:55.220 --> 28:56.270
Thank you.

28:57.610 --> 28:58.790
Sign first.

29:01.210 --> 29:04.730
[Rejection Notice
from the Capital Film Studio]

29:19.810 --> 29:20.340
Alright.

29:20.980 --> 29:23.710
He started strong,
ended up going downhill, huh?

29:24.180 --> 29:25.550
[Author: Xu Shengli] [Rejection]

29:30.830 --> 29:33.220
[The author of "As High as the Sky",
Xu Shengli] [Rejection]

29:35.260 --> 29:36.570
[The author of "As High as the Sky",
Xu Shengli] [Rejection]

29:48.070 --> 29:50.480
["As High as the Sky"]

29:53.770 --> 29:56.310
["As High as the Sky"]

30:05.230 --> 30:07.510
[The author of "As High as the Sky",
Xu Shengli] [Sixth Draft]

30:10.050 --> 30:10.740
How much is it?

30:10.740 --> 30:11.380
100 yuan.

30:11.570 --> 30:12.440
100 yuan?

30:12.480 --> 30:13.530
-It's too expensive.
-It's too expensive.

30:13.530 --> 30:14.750
You think that's expensive?

30:14.750 --> 30:15.940
You have good taste.

30:16.460 --> 30:17.460
This is made for export.

30:17.460 --> 30:18.720
Genuine export goods.

30:19.010 --> 30:19.440
[Music Conservatory Student Union]

30:19.460 --> 30:19.890
[Summer Work-Study
Program Registration Desk]

30:19.570 --> 30:20.090
This is our

30:20.090 --> 30:21.350
work-study program.

30:21.380 --> 30:22.330
Feel free to take a look.

30:21.440 --> 30:21.690
[Music Conservatory Student Union]

30:21.710 --> 30:21.910
[Summer Work-Study
Program Registration Desk]

30:22.210 --> 30:24.510
[CHUN LAI JIE]

30:22.590 --> 30:23.350
Right. If there's anything you don't know,

30:23.350 --> 30:24.420
you can ask me.

30:25.000 --> 30:25.900
Here is our

30:25.900 --> 30:26.750
training content.

30:26.750 --> 30:27.740
It includes product introduction,

30:27.740 --> 30:28.530
sales techniques,

30:28.530 --> 30:29.310
stall management,

30:29.310 --> 30:30.480
and things to note.

30:30.510 --> 30:31.440
The contact number is at the bottom.

30:31.170 --> 30:34.070
[CHUN LAI JIE]

30:31.510 --> 30:32.180
OK.

30:32.640 --> 30:33.070
Excuse me,

30:33.070 --> 30:34.570
would you like to learn about
the work-study program?

30:34.570 --> 30:35.170
Thank you.

30:36.250 --> 30:37.030
This is a program

30:37.030 --> 30:38.660
jointly organized by the school
and the local community,

30:38.660 --> 30:39.160
designed to

30:39.160 --> 30:40.220
make use of students' free time

30:40.220 --> 30:41.000
for work-study.

30:40.250 --> 30:40.600
[Music Conservatory Student Union]

30:40.620 --> 30:41.020
[Rules for the Summer Work-Study Program]

30:41.080 --> 30:41.980
[Organization and Purpose of the Program]
[Supply and Sales Arrangement]

30:42.000 --> 30:43.540
[Registration Requirements and Enrollment]
[Training Schedule]

30:44.480 --> 30:45.460
How do I sign up?

30:45.460 --> 30:46.440
Here is the application form.

30:46.440 --> 30:47.500
You can take a look.

30:47.590 --> 30:48.850
Then fill in your name,

30:48.900 --> 30:50.110
class, and student ID.

30:50.110 --> 30:51.830
We will organize training later.

30:51.830 --> 30:53.300
I'm not a student here.

30:53.570 --> 30:55.570
Print this out later.

30:55.700 --> 30:56.100
Right.

30:58.610 --> 31:01.210
Our Student Union
isn't open to the outsiders.

31:01.900 --> 31:02.600
Right.

31:02.750 --> 31:03.650
How about this?

31:03.790 --> 31:04.660
You can try the community channel instead.

31:04.660 --> 31:06.000
I'll give you the street office management
contact number.

31:06.000 --> 31:06.590
You can check with them first.

31:06.590 --> 31:07.180
Is that possible?

31:07.180 --> 31:07.630
Yes.

31:07.810 --> 31:09.210
That's great. Thank you.

31:12.420 --> 31:13.490
[Music Conservatory Student Union]

31:13.510 --> 31:14.700
[Summer Work-Study
Program Registration Desk]

31:27.620 --> 31:28.920
Little Northeasterner,

31:28.920 --> 31:30.440
the water isn't hot.

31:31.740 --> 31:33.340
Then wait for the next batch.

31:33.940 --> 31:36.070
It's only 30 degrees. It'll be a while.

31:37.050 --> 31:38.180
The food your dear sister saved for you.

31:38.180 --> 31:38.880
Have you eaten up?

31:38.880 --> 31:40.480
Don't talk nonsense.

31:43.530 --> 31:44.500
This is your first proper meal in days

31:44.500 --> 31:45.560
and it's just this?

31:46.700 --> 31:47.940
Everything tastes bland.

31:47.940 --> 31:48.940
I need something salty.

31:48.940 --> 31:50.740
Didn't you go to the film studio?

31:52.680 --> 31:54.140
Creative work takes time.

31:54.700 --> 31:56.920
I've got to be steady, step by step.
There's time.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.790
Got it. An artist, huh.

32:01.720 --> 32:02.310
Well...

32:02.590 --> 32:05.120
What about next month's rent?
Got it covered?

32:06.140 --> 32:07.190
Honestly,

32:07.420 --> 32:08.770
a lot of people who leave next month

32:08.770 --> 32:10.110
are in the same situation as you—

32:10.110 --> 32:11.110
barely managing,

32:11.140 --> 32:12.290
sometimes only one meal a day,

32:12.290 --> 32:13.550
not even daring to add an egg.

32:13.550 --> 32:14.280
Don't worry.

32:14.850 --> 32:16.380
I'll extend my stay
through the end of the year.

32:16.380 --> 32:16.850
Yes.

32:17.710 --> 32:18.910
I know your industry.

32:19.640 --> 32:20.520
Either nothing for months,

32:20.520 --> 32:21.960
or one job that keeps you
going for half a year.

32:21.960 --> 32:23.330
But who knows

32:23.480 --> 32:25.050
when the next gig will come, right?

32:25.050 --> 32:26.780
I don't do credit here, though.

32:27.280 --> 32:29.050
I've never been in debt in my life.

32:29.050 --> 32:30.510
This is really something.

32:30.570 --> 32:31.180
If I send my scripts

32:31.180 --> 32:32.410
to more film studios,

32:32.570 --> 32:33.970
I can also write articles

32:34.070 --> 32:35.420
and submit them to editorial departments,

32:35.420 --> 32:36.680
magazines, and newspapers.

32:36.680 --> 32:37.940
Those are all ways to make money.

32:37.940 --> 32:38.500
Yes.

32:39.480 --> 32:40.350
I mean

32:40.660 --> 32:42.050
we've got to think
both long-term and short-term,

32:42.050 --> 32:42.640
don't we?

32:43.150 --> 32:44.310
You've got ideals ahead of you,

32:44.310 --> 32:46.310
but in the near term
you still have to eat.

32:46.310 --> 32:48.640
Let's stay and then talk about the future.

33:02.900 --> 33:03.460
Zhuang.

33:05.400 --> 33:06.660
I was just looking for you

33:06.660 --> 33:07.590
and I ran into you here.

33:07.590 --> 33:08.450
Officer Zhang,

33:09.030 --> 33:10.360
you were looking for me?

33:13.000 --> 33:13.540
Look.

33:13.740 --> 33:15.070
Is this the bag you lost?

33:15.850 --> 33:16.800
Yes!

33:17.380 --> 33:19.040
You're an amazing detective.

33:20.850 --> 33:22.450
Did... Did you catch the guy?

33:22.880 --> 33:23.740
Not yet.

33:24.440 --> 33:25.860
A sanitation worker found it.

33:25.860 --> 33:26.920
Your ID was inside,

33:26.940 --> 33:28.270
along with some photos.

33:28.770 --> 33:30.370
The cash is definitely gone.

33:38.130 --> 33:39.680
You're smart, though—

33:40.220 --> 33:41.680
hiding money in a hidden layer.

33:41.680 --> 33:42.680
Here, sign this.

33:42.850 --> 33:43.250
OK.

33:46.610 --> 33:47.940
Thank you, Officer.

33:48.280 --> 33:49.430
You guys are incredible.

33:49.430 --> 33:50.360
You're welcome.

33:51.030 --> 33:51.510
Here.

33:52.510 --> 33:53.220
Thank you.

33:53.240 --> 33:53.880
Sorry for the trouble.

33:53.880 --> 33:54.480
It's fine.

33:54.660 --> 33:56.570
Consider that an unexpected gain.

33:56.570 --> 33:58.140
I'll contact you if there's news.

33:58.140 --> 33:58.780
Thank you.

33:59.180 --> 33:59.790
You're welcome.

33:59.790 --> 34:00.720
I appreciate it.

34:00.790 --> 34:01.390
By the way,

34:02.360 --> 34:04.090
if you have trouble in Beijing,

34:04.110 --> 34:04.810
call the police.

34:04.810 --> 34:05.290
OK!

34:10.969 --> 34:13.260
Will it work without turning on the stove?

34:13.260 --> 34:14.860
This is called a "onsen egg."

34:15.210 --> 34:16.400
You just soak the egg in water

34:16.400 --> 34:17.760
at about 60 to 80 degrees Celsius.

34:17.760 --> 34:18.710
The egg white

34:18.760 --> 34:20.370
sets slightly,

34:20.610 --> 34:22.010
but the yolk stays runny.

34:22.790 --> 34:24.790
It's delicious with some soy sauce.

34:25.480 --> 34:26.780
So that's an onsen egg?

34:27.710 --> 34:28.710
I thought it meant

34:29.010 --> 34:30.460
eating an egg

34:30.510 --> 34:32.170
while soaking in a hot spring.

34:32.880 --> 34:34.880
This egg has a better life than we do.

34:35.460 --> 34:37.659
Things will get better for us soon, too.

34:38.530 --> 34:39.460
Close your eyes.

34:45.400 --> 34:47.000
What are you thinking about?

35:17.000 --> 35:18.500
Where did you

35:18.500 --> 35:19.440
get this money?

35:23.220 --> 35:24.380
You got it back?

35:27.650 --> 35:28.850
The bulk of it is gone.

35:28.880 --> 35:29.550
But fortunately,

35:29.550 --> 35:30.550
I hid a little bit.

35:32.090 --> 35:33.220
You're impressive.

35:35.940 --> 35:36.800
This is for you.

35:38.380 --> 35:39.870
I don't need this much.

35:40.760 --> 35:42.420
Consider the rest a loan.

35:43.340 --> 35:43.960
No need.

35:44.000 --> 35:45.000
I submit articles every day.

35:45.000 --> 35:47.000
I'll get the royalties in a few days.

35:47.940 --> 35:49.530
I'm not that kind-hearted.

35:50.130 --> 35:51.460
I'm charging interest.

36:05.070 --> 36:07.000
This egg isn't having an easy time.

36:12.400 --> 36:14.000
Whether it has a good life or not

36:14.000 --> 36:16.090
depends on whether you
choose a passionate, intense life

36:16.090 --> 36:17.420
or a calm, ordinary one.

36:18.260 --> 36:19.730
That is well said.

36:20.550 --> 36:21.530
Whether it has a good life or not

36:21.530 --> 36:23.030
depends on whether you
choose a passionate, intense life

36:23.030 --> 36:24.360
or a calm, ordinary one.

36:24.980 --> 36:27.110
I gotta write that down when I get back.

36:27.770 --> 36:29.720
A passionate, intense life

36:31.170 --> 36:32.500
or a calm, ordinary one.

36:43.360 --> 36:44.070
I can see

36:45.230 --> 36:46.560
that you really love it.

36:46.760 --> 36:48.020
Just focus on writing.

36:49.570 --> 36:51.370
This money should tide you over.

36:51.460 --> 36:52.800
This weekend,

36:52.980 --> 36:54.380
I'll go check things out.

36:54.630 --> 36:55.960
If I can make some money,

36:56.840 --> 36:58.170
I can lend you a bit more.

36:59.400 --> 37:01.000
You found a way to make money?

37:02.340 --> 37:03.480
You go to class every day,

37:03.480 --> 37:04.840
yet you still have time
to figure this out?

37:04.840 --> 37:06.010
Even if I go to class,
I still need to solve

37:06.010 --> 37:07.340
my immediate problems.

37:10.320 --> 37:10.800
True.

37:11.000 --> 37:12.930
Dreams can't put food on the table.

37:14.210 --> 37:14.610
So,

37:14.920 --> 37:15.650
what exactly is your way

37:15.650 --> 37:16.760
of making money?

37:17.230 --> 37:18.440
I'm keeping it under wraps.

37:18.440 --> 37:19.770
Nothing is certain yet.

37:20.710 --> 37:22.640
Now you're keeping me in suspense.

37:26.630 --> 37:27.170
You two,

37:27.500 --> 37:28.210
what are you doing squatting here—

37:28.210 --> 37:29.170
hatching eggs?

37:30.340 --> 37:31.800
We're hatching golden eggs.

37:31.800 --> 37:32.840
Shiny and gold.

37:34.420 --> 37:36.550
Onsen eggs—golden and shiny.

37:37.070 --> 37:37.600
Alright.

37:37.960 --> 37:39.220
You two keep hatching.

37:40.920 --> 37:42.130
Here, try this.

37:43.380 --> 37:44.180
Look, the yolk

37:44.420 --> 37:45.290
is still runny.

37:45.690 --> 37:46.550
Slurp it first.

37:46.980 --> 37:47.380
Hurry.

37:47.980 --> 37:48.840
Is this cooked?

37:49.960 --> 37:50.420
This...

37:51.170 --> 37:52.370
This is an onsen egg.

37:52.400 --> 37:53.060
It's runny.

37:53.820 --> 37:56.020
Be careful. Don't spill it on yourself.

37:57.940 --> 37:58.470
How is it?

37:59.700 --> 38:00.800
It's like jelly.

38:03.200 --> 38:05.000
It's better with some soy sauce.

38:10.500 --> 38:12.450
Beat the hand drum and sing a song,

38:12.480 --> 38:15.500
I ride my horse over the mountain slopes.

38:17.110 --> 38:19.360
On the vast grasslands,
cattle and sheep grow strong,

38:19.360 --> 38:22.160
and golden waves
shimmer over the harvest fields.

38:25.010 --> 38:25.670
What are you doing?

38:25.670 --> 38:26.730
I'm waiting for you.

38:26.730 --> 38:27.570
Waiting for me?

38:27.570 --> 38:28.100
For what?

38:28.530 --> 38:30.990
Didn't you talk about
hatching golden eggs?

38:32.750 --> 38:34.410
You really took that to heart.

38:34.480 --> 38:36.540
How can I not care about making money?

38:36.570 --> 38:38.630
So, how do we hatch these golden eggs?

38:38.670 --> 38:39.630
It's not decided yet.

38:39.630 --> 38:40.330
No, no, no.

38:40.530 --> 38:41.530
Sit down.

38:41.690 --> 38:42.420
Just sit.

38:42.590 --> 38:43.920
Stop keeping me in suspense.

38:43.920 --> 38:45.110
Just tell me.

38:46.400 --> 38:46.930
Alright.

38:49.070 --> 38:49.920
I found a spot

38:50.170 --> 38:51.070
near a school

38:51.130 --> 38:53.060
where I can set up a clothing stall.

38:53.130 --> 38:54.380
The daily stall fee

38:54.380 --> 38:55.440
is only a few dozen yuan.

38:55.440 --> 38:56.300
I'll use the rest of the money

38:56.300 --> 38:57.460
to stock up.

38:57.570 --> 38:58.820
Then if I mark up each item

38:58.820 --> 38:59.610
by three to five yuan,

38:59.610 --> 39:00.670
I'll make a profit.

39:03.690 --> 39:04.690
A stall

39:05.010 --> 39:05.810
near a school?

39:07.230 --> 39:09.490
Those spots must be in high demand.

39:09.610 --> 39:11.190
Besides, with so many stalls,

39:11.190 --> 39:12.340
can we make any money?

39:12.340 --> 39:13.670
We have to give it a shot.

39:14.630 --> 39:15.630
Getting this money back

39:15.630 --> 39:17.030
was a pleasant surprise.

39:17.880 --> 39:19.170
I'll use this 400 yuan

39:19.260 --> 39:20.670
as startup capital.

39:22.170 --> 39:23.170
I'm confident.

39:28.280 --> 39:29.340
What are you doing?

39:30.880 --> 39:31.410
500 yuan.

39:31.920 --> 39:32.580
Either make

39:32.920 --> 39:33.530
or break.

39:41.190 --> 39:41.720
Let's go!

39:42.010 --> 39:42.540
Let's go.

39:44.070 --> 39:45.130
Where are we going?

39:45.150 --> 39:46.080
To buy goods.

39:46.360 --> 39:47.730
Where are we buying them?

39:47.730 --> 39:48.130
Guess.

39:48.500 --> 39:49.100
Me? Guess?

39:50.050 --> 39:51.460
Then how much are we buying?

39:51.460 --> 39:52.000
Guess.

39:52.500 --> 39:53.630
Wait... We are partners;

39:53.630 --> 39:54.570
why won't you tell me anything?

39:54.570 --> 39:57.140
[CHUN LAI JIE]

39:57.190 --> 40:04.300
[Develop Campus Services,
Boost Economic Growth]

39:58.670 --> 39:59.200
I'm back.

40:00.110 --> 40:00.510
Boss,

40:01.000 --> 40:02.320
is it okay to place the rack like this?

40:02.320 --> 40:02.900
It's fine.

40:02.900 --> 40:03.900
Hang the clothes.

40:05.230 --> 40:05.690
Come on.

40:06.400 --> 40:07.610
I looked at the other stalls

40:07.610 --> 40:09.300
packed with goods

40:09.320 --> 40:09.960
and have so many different items.

40:09.960 --> 40:11.320
Can we really make it
with just this little stock?

40:11.320 --> 40:13.260
Quality matters more than quantity.

40:13.260 --> 40:14.260
If I match and style them properly,

40:14.260 --> 40:15.840
we won't be worse than anyone else.

40:15.840 --> 40:16.440
Hang it up.

40:16.650 --> 40:17.210
OK.

40:17.380 --> 40:18.340
Two-piece outfits go on the left,

40:18.340 --> 40:19.670
dresses go on the right.

40:19.690 --> 40:20.090
OK.

40:22.760 --> 40:23.890
This one goes up too.

40:36.170 --> 40:36.900
Hang it here?

40:39.940 --> 40:40.710
Give that to me.

40:40.710 --> 40:41.440
Give it to me.

40:44.130 --> 40:45.440
Put this on.

40:45.500 --> 40:46.230
I put it on?

40:46.300 --> 40:46.790
Yes.

40:46.900 --> 40:47.840
We haven't even opened for business yet,

40:47.840 --> 40:48.820
and you're already giving me a piece?

40:48.820 --> 40:49.690
In your dreams.

40:49.900 --> 40:50.430
Put it on.

40:51.030 --> 40:52.010
I just walked around

40:52.010 --> 40:53.360
and noticed every stall

40:53.380 --> 40:54.880
has those mannequin models.

40:54.880 --> 40:56.280
We're going to do a real-life version—

40:56.280 --> 40:57.800
more vivid, more eye-catching.

40:57.800 --> 40:58.760
That works.

41:06.070 --> 41:07.130
Put it on over here.

41:10.050 --> 41:11.550
Ma'am, can I use your mirror?

41:11.550 --> 41:13.010
-Yes, please.
-Thank you.

41:13.230 --> 41:13.830
Like this?

41:15.030 --> 41:16.170
Fix the collar properly.

41:16.170 --> 41:16.610
OK.

41:17.400 --> 41:18.280
Button it up.

41:18.730 --> 41:19.460
Button it up.

41:19.630 --> 41:20.920
Then tuck it into your pants.

41:20.920 --> 41:21.280
OK.

41:23.340 --> 41:24.150
How much we can sell

41:24.150 --> 41:25.030
this shirt for today

41:25.030 --> 41:26.000
depends on your performance.

41:26.000 --> 41:27.660
Then... Why don't you wear it?

41:27.730 --> 41:28.460
Cut the crap.

41:28.960 --> 41:30.160
Roll up your sleeves.

41:30.630 --> 41:31.530
Thank you, ma'am.

41:31.530 --> 41:32.520
It's fine.

41:33.190 --> 41:34.050
You look sharp.

41:34.650 --> 41:35.230
Thank you.

41:35.230 --> 41:35.830
It's fine.

41:39.180 --> 41:39.810
Boss,

41:40.440 --> 41:41.930
since we're new here,

41:42.000 --> 41:42.670
should I go

41:42.710 --> 41:43.550
to the nearby vendors

41:43.550 --> 41:44.350
and say hello?

41:44.460 --> 41:46.000
That way we can look out for each other.

41:46.000 --> 41:47.460
Why didn't I think of that?

41:48.760 --> 41:49.590
Then buy some water

41:49.590 --> 41:50.480
and bring it to them.

41:50.480 --> 41:51.400
Just deduct it from the petty cash.

41:51.400 --> 41:51.860
No need.

41:52.420 --> 41:54.020
I'll use my own little stash.

41:56.920 --> 41:57.710
Come back again!

41:57.710 --> 41:58.420
OK. Thank you, sis.

41:58.420 --> 41:59.460
I'll save a nice one for you.

41:59.460 --> 41:59.900
OK.

42:01.150 --> 42:02.760
This won't do.

42:02.820 --> 42:04.620
You have to move the stall aside.

42:04.710 --> 42:05.670
Or you'll block the path.

42:05.670 --> 42:06.840
You can't lack public spirit.

42:06.840 --> 42:07.790
Right?

42:08.110 --> 42:08.950
Your two shops

42:08.980 --> 42:09.820
are too close together.

42:09.820 --> 42:11.260
Don't block other people's business.

42:11.260 --> 42:11.480
OK.

42:11.480 --> 42:12.680
That won't do either.

42:12.900 --> 42:13.920
Don't litter.

42:13.960 --> 42:14.670
Don't throw trash around.

42:14.670 --> 42:15.470
Do you hear me?

42:16.980 --> 42:17.840
I think you guys

42:17.880 --> 42:19.540
-sell this in summer...
-Sis.

42:19.860 --> 42:20.460
Young man,

42:21.650 --> 42:22.500
you mentioned

42:22.980 --> 42:24.170
that Wenzhou girl just now…

42:24.170 --> 42:24.760
Hello.

42:26.280 --> 42:28.760
This girl is really pretty.

42:28.840 --> 42:30.130
Are you from Wenzhou too?

42:30.130 --> 42:30.780
Yes.

42:31.690 --> 42:32.820
So nice. So pretty.

42:33.050 --> 42:33.820
Thank you.

42:34.040 --> 42:40.040
[Trendy Clothing Shop]

42:34.140 --> 42:34.630
Look.

42:34.820 --> 42:36.020
My shop is right here.

42:36.940 --> 42:37.630
My child

42:37.690 --> 42:39.050
studies at the conservatory,

42:39.050 --> 42:40.210
so I'm here accompanying him.

42:40.210 --> 42:41.230
Such a big shop—

42:41.670 --> 42:42.530
impressive.

42:43.190 --> 42:44.500
It's all thanks to the students.

42:44.500 --> 42:45.460
We Wenzhou people are very united

42:45.460 --> 42:46.730
when we do clothing business

42:46.730 --> 42:47.630
away from home.

42:47.960 --> 42:48.550
From now on,

42:48.550 --> 42:49.280
